description: Join the South Boston community, living minutes from the Broadway Red Line T, shops, dining and nightlife including Loco, Capo and Lincoln. Stunning 2 bed, 1 bath residence blends historic charm with modern style, featuring exposed brick, 10'+ ceilings, wide pine floors, and arched windows. Expansive living room with gas fireplace flows seamlessly into a open dining area, perfect for entertaining. Chef’s kitchen is outfitted with top-tier appliances including a Wolf range, Sub-Zero refrigerator and stone countertops. Luxurious, renovated bathroom features marble floors, a double marble vanity and a walk-in mosaic-tiled shower. Both bedrooms offer large closets with built-ins, and a marble mantel in the primary. Enjoy in-unit laundry, a large private storage unit & a professionally managed, pet-friendly association. Rare opportunity to own a beautifully restored Southie home with financial incentives to make it even more attainable.
